Package: scMetaTraj
Type: Package
Title: Metabolic State Space and Trajectory Analysis for Single-Cell Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("YourName", "Here", email = "your@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    scMetaTraj provides a framework for modeling cellular metabolic states 
    and continuous metabolic trajectories using pathway-level scoring.
    The package enables lineage-restricted metabolic analysis, 
    metabolic pseudotime inference, module-level trend analysis, 
    and visualization of metabolic state transitions.
